name: karate
description: The file karate.gml contains the network of friendships between the 34 members of a karate club at a US university.

graph.semantic: The file karate.gml contains the network of friendships between the 34 members of a karate club at a US university.

qares.question: which node has the highest degree in the graph?
qares.query: SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.grap@erch6n graph.property.contain_nodes ?e1. e1? node.property.degree ?e2} ORDER BY DESC(?e2) LIMIT 1

qares.question: what is the node with the lowest centrality in the graph?
qares.query: SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.grap@erch6n graph.property.contain_nodes ?e1. e1? node.property.degree_centrality ?e2} ORDER BY (?e2) LIMIT 1

qares.question: what is the node with the highest centrality that links with node “1”?
qares.query: SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.node@1 node.property.link_with ?e1. e1? node.property.degree_centrality ?e2} ORDER BY DESC(?e2) LIMIT 1

qares.question: what is the node with the lowest centrality in community 1?
qares.query: SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.comm@qfhptp community.property.contain_nodes ?e1. e1? node.property.degree_centrality ?e2} ORDER BY (?e2) LIMIT 1
